Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're up to,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but why don't you do that \Nfor the living instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd save more people that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that easy to save people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, what you're doing is a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're never getting anywhere with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghoul?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me... Why not you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You're so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrifying you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:55.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんた…何のつもりか知らんが、
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:59.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうせなら生きているモンにやってやっちゃあどうだい。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:02.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのほうがよっぽど人助けだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:08.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人は…そう簡単には救えぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:15.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だからって無駄がすぎるんじゃあねぇかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:29.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいおい…賽の河原じゃあるめぇし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:32.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんた…一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:41.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あやかしか！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:03.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…あんた！な、なん…で…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:08.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すまない…わしにも…わからぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:10.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前…お前はなんと…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:14.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんと…凄まじい…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayed this world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And it simmers within
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupturing my innards
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Swelling a reddish black
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the sun burnt skin ruptures
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:04:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light \Nin the depths of the seething darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices \Nin the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light \Nin the depths of the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices \Nin the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,#17 The story of questions and answers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's real human skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can smile now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can speak. What a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes, I see they're still blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I met you, gave you a body, \Nand named you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But did I do the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:06:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As you defeated it, it was almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, it's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I use it to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I want another. The same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This. I want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'll fix you something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There, it's done. Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I can feel heat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold, too. I feel it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Old habits die hard. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The string has become brittle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me change it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your only key to finding your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Daigo Kagemitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Daigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You met the man of this family crest? \NThe man that is your...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He fed me to the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru, tell me what you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What did the man of this crest tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake, my lady. \NI will call for the doctor right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How naive I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, your mother has awoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What great news! Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am in a hurry. \NI will see her when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He could've visited his mother \Nbefore we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghoul was sighted in our territory. \NHe had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's right. Young Master has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, a whole domain \Nis weighing on your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How heavy the load...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I found and raised you, \Nonly to make you live in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I cannot give you a new leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You will go fight demons again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You will defeat them and regain your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And the domain you bear \Non your shoulders...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that responsibility is \Nfor your father, the lord, to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You may look more human than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But have you not become less human \Non the inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I saw, I assume that ghouls \Nare not the only things you've killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A new prosthetic leg \Nwould only take you closer to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor said you should be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Never do such a foolish thing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, how truly foolish I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I offered my life, \Nbut what worth does my life have?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember \Nthe headless Goddess of Mercy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the one you always prayed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It lost its head when Hyakkimaru was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a gift, a token of faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept praying to it for my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard that he was alive, \NI thought my prayers had been answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How vain I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru survived,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,only because the Goddess offered its head \Nto the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else would his head still be intact \Nwhen all else was taken from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt it, plain as day, \Nwhen the Goddess's head was smashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That among the 12 demons, \Nthere was one that failed to eat my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the Goddess of Mercy is cracked, \Nyour deal has been broken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru shall surely regain his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And the prosperity of this land \Nshall cease, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You are overthinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest up and get well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep close watch over the Hall of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,About Hyakkimaru's whereabouts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There has been a sighting of \Nthe kid he was with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Have Tahomaru go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, my lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody seems to be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A merchant family and some servants \Nlive here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But nobody's seen them for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not since the ghoul was first sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There are openings for air \Nand enough supplies for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru, you asked me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it that you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you leave this cave, \Nyou'll go back to a world of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still wish to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Do you want a body? \N-I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You have something other people don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A human body may only become \Na burden to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-And you still want one? \N-I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why? \N-You've never thought about why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So every last demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Young Master! \N-A ghoul rat. Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo! You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's quick. \N-I've maimed it. Stay alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Your body is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need a reason \Nto want to get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But demons won't be \Nthe only things you'll have to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father, mother, \Nand your younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of Daigo, too. \NThey'll all try to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When that happens, the body you regain \Nwill be stained with human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It will weigh heavy on you, \Nheavier than any prosthetic limb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you still be human then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left beside you \Nwill be lifeless corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be all alone in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-Alone? \N-Yes, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-I fear that... \N-No. There is somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-It killed humans to raise its children. \N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Foul creature, prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd saved that poor little baby, \Nbut all I did
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,was make it float down \Nthe river of hell again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be just another demon to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-Young Master. \N-We'll kill it. Hyogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you flee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-I shall slay it. \N-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If we keep the parent alive, \Nthe babies will stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghoul or not, I can't agree with \Nthe way you're handling this, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hyogo. \N-Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutsu. Hyogo. Never again will I let \Nmy feelings blunt my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do anything to protect this land \Nand its people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:19:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You said there was somebody \Nwho will stay by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't have to tell me. \NIt is enough that you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is somebody in your life \Nthat is not your enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that person may be able to keep you human.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, you never used it \Nwhen you lived with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is... No, you needn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're "Mama."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly you. That's not what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. \NI wasn't alive in your eyes until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I still have the right to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe our lord is making \NYoung Master go kill Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It is for the good of the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not let my feelings guide me \Nany longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:22:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru has been sighted \Naround Sodegahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We will go there and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,March!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.63,0:22:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:06.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,確かに人のものだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:10.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,笑えるのだなお前！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしの声も聞こえるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:14.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞こえる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:19.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,喋れる！なんということだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,目は…まだ見えぬようだが…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:25.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも…感じる。ずっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:28.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ずっと…感じてた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだ…わしは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:36.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしはお前の…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:41.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前の…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何なのだろうな…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:51.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前に出会い…人の体を与え、名付けはしたが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:56.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それが果たしてお前にとって…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:06:00.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれは…まるで
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:06.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:08.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ…壊れたようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:10.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦いに使った。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:13.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だから、同じものを…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:16.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,腹が減ってるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これを…これが…欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まずは…何か食わねばな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:04.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぁできたぞ。少し待っておれよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:10.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫。熱いのはわかる。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:13.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,冷たいのも、全部わかる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうか…そうだったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:19.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クセは抜けぬものだ。さぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:29.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,紐がもろくなっておるな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,新しいものに取り替えてやろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:35.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,前の出生に繋がる唯一のものだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐…景光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:39.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:45.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,会ったのか！その家紋の主に！それがお前の…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:48.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おれを鬼神に喰わせた…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだ喰ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それは一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:59.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸！聞いたままでよい。話してみよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:04.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,。家紋の主は、そなたに何を語ったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:20.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,御方様！お目覚めになりましたか！すぐに薬師を
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:30.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わたくしは…どこまでも甘い…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:36.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若様！御方様がお目覚めに！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:40.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おぉ！それは重畳！若！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:44.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,急ぐ用があるゆえ、戻ったらお目にかかる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:53.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お母上のお顔ぐらい、見てからにすればよいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:57.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ご領内にあやかしが出たのだ。仕方あるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若は変わられた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:00.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが…確かに。以前とは…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:31.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,つまり…お前ひとりに国ひとつがのしかかっているということか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんと重い…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:46.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前を拾い生かしたのは地獄を味わわせるためだったか…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:58.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれがいる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:00.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれが欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:07.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,できぬ。新しい足はやれぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:11.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前はまた鬼神との戦いにゆくだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神を倒し身体を取り戻し、
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:17.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そしてお前に乗っている国は…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:22.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや、それは領主であるお前の父が責めを負えばよいことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:28.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,確かにお前は、姿は人に近づいたのかもしれん。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:32.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だがその実、人から遠ざかってはおらぬか。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:39.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの様子…お前が殺めてきたのはあやかしだけではあるまい。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしにはわかる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:56.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,新しい義足は、お前をまた地獄へ近づけるだけだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしにはできん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:02.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺は…欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:03.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すまぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:17.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:23.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしは…お前を救えぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,救えぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:29.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,救えませぬ！わたくしは、そなたを！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:43.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,薬師がもう心配はいらぬと申しておった。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:47.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,二度とあのような愚かな真似はいたすな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まこと愚かにございました。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:54.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わたくしの命など、何の足しにもならぬものを。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:57.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:01.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,首なしの菩薩像を覚えておられましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:04.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ。常日頃拝んでおったな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:08.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの首が消えたのは、百鬼丸が生まれたとき。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:13.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,たくしは、これこそ信心の賜物と。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:16.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その後もずっとあの子の無事を祈り続け
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:21.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生きているとわかったときは、母の思いが通じたのだと。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:26.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんという思い上がり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:31.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿。百鬼丸が生きていたは、
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:35.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの菩薩像が身代わりとして鬼神に喰われたためにございます。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:40.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうでなければなぜ、すべてを奪われたあの子の頭が残っておりましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:47.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの菩薩像が砕けたとき、はっきりと感じたのでございます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:53.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,12の鬼神のうち、あの子を喰い損ねたものがいると。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:58.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,菩薩像が砕けた今、殿との約定は破れました
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:03.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そして、百鬼丸はきっと己の身体を取り戻すでしょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:09.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿。この国の安寧の時は…終わりまする
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたの思い過ごしじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,早く身体を治せ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:30.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おるか。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:35.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,地獄堂に見張りを付け、どんな異変も見逃すな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:39.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それと、百鬼丸の行方にございますが。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:42.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれが連れていた子供を見つけたとの知らせが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸に行かせよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:48.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それが…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人の気配がないな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:57.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,庁屋の一家と使用人が何名かいたそうですが、
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:59.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ぱったりと姿を見せなくなったとか。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あやかしが出始めた頃とのことです
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:05.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:13.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いますね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:33.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,焦ることはない。風穴はあるし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:39.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,食料や水も、まだいくらかはある
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:42.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸。なぜと言ったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしもお前に問おう。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:47.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜだ。なぜ戦う。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:52.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここを出れば、また修羅の世界に戻ることになる。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それでも出たいか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,出たい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:59.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,身体が欲しいのか\N欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:03.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前は人にない力を持っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:10.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人並みの身体は、むしろお前を不自由に縛るかもしれん。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:12.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それでも欲しいか\N欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:14.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:19.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ？\N考えたことはないか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺の…ものだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:27.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だから鬼神は…全部…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:30.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殺す！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:36.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若！\N化けネズミだ。抜かるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫！おのれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,素早い！\N手負いにした。気をそらすな！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:58.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:02.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,確かにお前の身体はお前のものだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:05.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,取り戻すのに理由はいらぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:09.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが殺すのは、鬼神やあやかしだけでは済むまい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:14.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前の父母\Nそして…弟も
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:19.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐の民も、必ずお前の邪魔をするだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:25.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うなれば、お前が取り戻す身体は人の血にまみれたものになる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:30.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それは…義手や義足よりも…重い。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:34.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのときお前は人であり得るのか\N少なくとも…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:39.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前のそばにあるのは屍だけになりはせぬか。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:42.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この世に…お前1人だけに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:46.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,1人…\Nそう。1人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:53.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしにはそれが…\N違う。いる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:54.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,誰がいるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今は…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:05.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今はいない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:17.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:25.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,子を育てるために…人を？\Nなに？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おのれ物の怪、覚悟！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:10.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしは…あの哀れな赤ん坊を救ったつもりで、
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:13.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,再び修羅の川に流しただけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:15.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:21.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前にとって、わしもまた鬼神の1人なのかもしれぬな…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:30.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若！\N片付けるぞ！兵庫！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:33.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,逃がさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:24.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いかがします？若
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:26.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひと思いに\N待て
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:28.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,火をかけろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:33.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,親をこのままにしておけば、子も逃げまい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:41.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若…いくらあやかしでも、俺はこのやり方は好きじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫\N帰るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:53.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陸奥。兵庫。私は二度と…剣を情で鈍らせることはしない。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:58.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この国を…民を、守るために！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:19:59.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これでよい。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:12.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,誰かいると言っておったな。お前のそばにいる者か…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:16.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いい。お前がわかっていれば、それでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:21.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前に殺す以外の存在がある。もしかしたらその者が、
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:24.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前を人に留めてくれるやもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:29.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:32.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わ…わしの名か！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:37.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一緒に暮らしていたときは名で呼ぶこともなかったからな…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:41.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしは…いや…知らんでよい。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:43.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしは何者でもない。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:49.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,知ってる。これが何というものか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん、だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:03.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バカ…それは違うぞ…違…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:32.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうか…これまでお前たちには、\Nわしなど生きたものと見えていなかったか。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:37.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだ死ぬ資格があったとはな…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:45.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸討伐に若を向かわせるのか、殿は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:48.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫。国事ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:51.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや…俺も腹を決めた。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:54.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若と同じ。情は持ち込まぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:22:00.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸の一味が、袖ヶ浜にいたと知らせがあった。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:04.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただちに赴き、これを討つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:08.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,出陣！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.63,0:22:22.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.74,0:22:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Born into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The distorted shape of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet it beats courageously
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from the path of evil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.97,0:23:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing the withering seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.43,0:23:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We search for the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In our ugliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.35,0:23:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even recognize the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.81,0:23:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As we peel back the skin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We are forever tormented by our stupidity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the dawn never comes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the painful night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You who distrusts nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to love \Nthis accursed world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we carry the world \Non our shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to take it back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.10,0:23:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ayakashigi"
